name: Sandesh Engineers
overview:
Founded in the year 1991, at Pune (Maharashtra, India), we, “Sandesh Engineers, Pune”, are recognized as a reputed name engaged in manufacturing and supplying a comprehensive assortment of dies, molds, jigs, fixtures, tooling and VMC machine components. etc.

My Catalog : Our offered range includes Jigs and Fixture, CNC-Machining Fixture, Dies, Press Tools and Dies, Forging Dies, Die Cast Tooling, Die Casting Die Design, Press Tools, Precision Press Parts Tools, Injection Moulds, Socket Eye, VMC Machine Components, Plastic Moulds, Letter Punches, etc.

Our Team: Our highly experienced and diligent team of experts assists us in offering the high quality range of dies and machine components. Our professionals are highly experienced and knowledgeable in meeting the variegated demands of the clients.

Client Satisfaction: Owing to our hard work of personnel, we have established ourselves strongly in the national market. We are backed by skilled and experienced team of professionals which enables to manufacture our wide range of products in complete compliance with client specifications.

Why Us?: We are placed at a reputable position in the industry by offering the supreme quality dies and machine components to our clients at reasonable costs. Owing to the following reasons, we have got an edge over other market players:

Advanced infrastructure
Adopting latest industry trends
